OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"I'm hoping (for) more awareness
OL,8,Fbecause if I knew about it sooner then
OL,9,FI would have gone to hospital sooner,"
OL,10,Fsays Keeleigh Goodwin.
OL,12,FEarlier in March, Keeleigh, 21, was
OL,13,Famong more than a dozen people
OL,14,Fhospitalised after a deadly meningitis
OL,15,Foutbreak in Canterbury, in Kent.
OL,17,FThe outbreak killed two students.
OL,26,@oD@MpmoD@Qpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
