FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FKeeleigh, who is now recovering at
OL,8,Fhome with her family, told ITV
OL,9,FMeridian of the "scary" ordeal she
OL,10,Funderwent, explaining she had been
OL,11,Fleft with "a lot of anxiety".
OL,13,FShe said: "It's definitely been scary,
OL,14,Flike the fact I could have died or
OL,15,Flike my life could have been changed
OL,16,Ffully, and like the fact people have
OL,17,Fdied from it... it's a lot to process
OL,18,Fas well."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FKeeleigh, despite her concerns, has
OL,8,Fsaid she will return to work on
OL,9,FTuesday, and has spoke of her hope
OL,10,Fthat lessons can be learned by health
OL,11,Fofficials around awareness and
OL,12,Feducation of meningitis.
OL,14,FThe outbreak in Kent was identified to
OL,15,Fhave been started by the meningitis B
OL,16,Fstrain of the disease, for which a
OL,17,Fvaccine was only introduced on the NHS
OL,18,Ffor babies in 2015.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe majority of young people born
OL,8,Fbefore then are not protected against
OL,9,Fit unless they have had the jab
OL,10,Fprivately.
OL,12,FThousands of meningitis B vaccines
OL,13,Fwere subsequently rolled out to
OL,14,Fstudents living on the University of
OL,15,FKent campus.
OL,17,FBut Keeleigh argues that inoculations
OL,18,Fagainst the strain should be made
OL,19,Favailable for anyone who wants them
OL,20,Fbecause meningitis B is "such a
OL,21,Fserious, life-changing illness".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
