PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FShe has also asked employers of others
OL,8,Faffected by the Kent outbreak to show
OL,9,Fpatience as they continue to recover.
OL,11,F"I think people just need to be a
OL,12,Flittle patient and understanding, and
OL,13,FI hope that other workplaces will be
OL,14,Faccommodating to other people that
OL,15,Fhave been affected in terms of like
OL,16,Fputting things in place for them,"
OL,17,FKeeleigh said.
OL,19,F"I've been lucky that mine have been
OL,20,Ffairly accommodating and hopefully the
OL,21,Fothers will have the same."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
