PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIn a previous interview with ITV
OL,8,FMeridian, Keeleigh said she owed her
OL,9,Flife to her housemates, who called for
OL,10,Fan ambulance after she had collapsed
OL,11,Fand suffered a seizure.
OL,13,FShe also explained how she and her
OL,14,Fmother had initially believed
OL,15,FKeeleigh's symptoms to resemble those
OL,16,Fof Covid, adding they were they were
OL,17,Fshocked after she was diagnosed with
OL,18,Fmeningitis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FShe said: "I didn't know much about it
OL,8,Fbecause you know it's not really
OL,9,Fsomething you think you'd get.
OL,11,F"Obviously I knew it was quite a
OL,12,Fserious illness, disease, so I've been
OL,13,Fput on a drip of fluids and IV and
OL,14,Fantibiotics for the treatment which is
OL,15,Fmeant to last seven to ten days so I
OL,16,Fhave to remain in hospital in an
OL,17,Fisolated room for that amount of time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774980701
OL,3,CKent meningitis survivor hopes for
OL,4,C'more awareness' of disease after
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"It's been quite a scary experience -
OL,8,Fthe fact that I almost could have died
OL,9,Fif I hadn't been found or if the
OL,10,Fseizure had happened in my sleep.
OL,12,F"It's definitely changed my outlook of
OL,13,Flife."
OL,15,FThe latest update from the UKHSA
OL,16,Fshowed that, as of Thursday, March 26,
OL,17,Fsome 22 cases of meningitis - 20
OL,18,Fconfirmed and two under investigation
OL,19,F- had been reported in Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
